                        <item xml:id="a1">
                           <locus target="#15rb">Fol. 15rb</locus>: Supplication for the
                           commissioners and the scribe.<q xml:lang="gez">Fol. 15rb: ኦአኃውየ፡ ደቂቀ፡ ዛቲ፡
                              መቅደስ፡ ኢትርስኡነ፡ በጊዜ፡ አንበብክምዋ፡ ለዛቲ፡ መጽሐፍ፡ ለአግብርቲክሙ፡ ተስፋ፡ ጽዮን፡ መርደ፡ ክዮስ፡
                              ግደ፡ ማርያም፡ ወለጸሐፊሐ፡ ኃጥእ፡ ዘድንግል፡፡</q>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/> Written in the main hand. The note mentions the names
                           Täsfa Ṣǝyon, Märdä Kǝyos, Gǝdä Maryam and the name of the scribe
                           zä-Dǝngǝl. </item>
                        <item xml:id="a2">
                           <locus target="#112rb">Fol. 112rb</locus>: Ownership note.<q xml:lang="gez">Fol. 112rb: ዛቲ፡ መጽሐፈ፡ ፍትሐት፡ ዘቅዱስ፡ ሚካኤል፡ ዘአጋምዮ፡ ዘሠረቃ፡
                              ወዘፈሐቃ፡ ወዘተአገላ፡ ወዘአልሃላ፡ ውጉዘ፡ ለይኩን፡ በቃለ፡ ፫፻፲ወ፰ርቱዓነ፡ ሃይማኖት፡ ወፈድፋደ፡ ይኩን፡
                              መክፈልቱ፡ ምስለ፡ አርዮስ፡ ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡ አሜን፡፡</q>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/> Written in the main hand. The note mentions the church
                           of Qǝddus Mikaʾel ʾAgamyo as the owner of the Ms. </item>
                        <item xml:id="e1">- Pen trials: fols. 1v, 2r. &#xD; - Minor notes in the
                           margins: fols. 1v, 25v.&#xD; - Words እገሌ and እገሊት, "so-and-so" are marked
                           by thin lines above and below throughout the Ms.&#xD; - Space for
                           rubricated names left unfilled: fols. 9va, 10ra, 10va, 12vb, 18va, 35v,
                           44ra, 46ra, 50va, 51ra, 73va, 107rb.&#xD; - Corrections written
                           interlineally: fols. 28rb, 42va, 43va, 44vb, 74vb, 84va, 86va, 92ra,
                           97vb, 113rb.&#xD; - Immediate correction marked by thin lines above and
                           below words: fols. 35r, 103va.&#xD; - The scribe used compressed script
                           in fols. 112va-116vb.</item>
                     </list>
